{"tid":1772220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（encore）法國工會號召下星期二再次罷工","createTime":"2019-12-06T12:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T12:27:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bea841e4b9c75b8014d1372eaddc1a9aff8a6f21","tid":1772220,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T12:17:54.000Z","msg":"法國爆發20多年來最大規模的全國大罷工後，工會號召民眾下星期二再次罷工，反對總統馬克龍計劃改革退休制度。<br />\n<br />\n法國最大的公共部門工會，與另外三個工會開會後，宣布下星期二再次採取工業行動，號召民眾上街抗議。工會代表批評，政府仍未清楚社會的不滿，最好盡快找出解決問題的辦法。<br />\n<br />\n法國多個城市星期四都有民眾遊行，政府估計全國有超過80萬人上街。法國總工會說，全國有140多萬人罷工，首都巴黎與多個城市爆發警民衝突，多人被捕。總統府愛麗舍宮說，馬克龍堅持改革，但願意傾聽與協商。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496377-20191206.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496377-20191206.htm&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqruUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=f0849097\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496377-20191206.htm&h=747375ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496377-20191206.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a90692d7a036caa94991a1cfb1f46ab4a5d3a63c","tid":1772220,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T12:27:23.000Z","msg":"傾聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}